room_title: Escape room "The Dig" by Paranoia Quest in Atlanta
room_address: 3333 Buford Drive NE, Suite VB03, Buford GA 30519
room_description: You are in a team of archaeologists. At first, you will find yourself in a mining shaft, and the only way you can leave is by finding the lost Aztec temple deep beneath the surface and having fulfilled all tasks. Can you and your fellow adventurers find the clues, solve the puzzles, and unravel the mystery of the secret temple before it's too late?
